name: Cum Bath
description:
This is my fourth LoRa model, it's made in collaboration with gronon.

Tips: scale 1 must be good
Training model: NAI
Model i used to generate images: abyssorangemix2_Hard
Keywords: cum bathed

You can add or remove as you wish: cum on hair, cum on face, bathtub, tentacles (not all of this tags will work good, except cum on face and cum on hair).
Even with perfect prompt, don't forget that the concept is for the girl to be in a cum bath, not in the sea, not in the entrance, in the bath

If you want to help me with learning how to create LoRA models, or learn to create models with me - please join my server in discord, my goal is to create a friendly community that will help each other to achieve high quality training for LoRA models.
discord.gg/vmVzJQEhqy

If u know how to improve model, let me know
